name: S. S.
summary: Led No-Code Application development, significantly reducing dev time at Media.net.

workExperience.description: Led the development of a No-Code Application using ReactJs, TypeScript, Zustand, enabling developers to swiftly create templates, significantly reducing development time from 5 days to 1 hour. Wireframed and Developed reusable and editable table component with complex filters, incorporated tools and integrated APIs to manage ad campaign cost of 10,000+ customers. Created a location filter plugins with OpenStreetMap integration for 5+ WordPress sites using PHP and JavaScript, utilizing ES6 methods. Collaborate with Product Managers, Web Designers and Software Engineers to deliver compelling 10+ user-facing blog websites. Conducted peer code reviews. Built a tool to efficiently manage and clone ad templates across over 30 GitLab repos. Utilized ReactJS, GitLab APIs and Google OAuth, reducing developer workload from 18 hours to 2 hours.

Debugged and resolved canvas rendering issue, resulting in loading speed by 70%. Implemented comprehensive unit and integration testing strategies using Jest in NodeJs. Integrated Two-Factor Authentication, following protocols to enhancing app security through both email and Twilio SMS integration for 1000+ businesses. Integrated Google Maps with dynamic elements, crafted reusable and scalable components for seamless user location retrieval, and implemented captivating custom map pin logic. Upgraded Angular 9 to 12, fixing package issues, which resulted in % improved page load. Built user tours and on-boarding using Shephard and wrote necessary APIs in NodeJS, to improve user experience.
